cc:Work.dc:title: Adjustable wrench - icon style
cc:Work.dc:description: This is a remix of http://openclipart.org/media/files/method/5077, however I could not link it. Details, shadows and highlights have been added for presentablility and thicker edges have been applied in order to make it more visible in icon sizes. The base SVG has been put into Public Domain by author jannev (http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Image:Adjustable_wrench.svg)
